Tutorial Cloud Foundry Environment in BTP

1. In BTP COCKPIT, go to Entitlements
2. Click Edit -> Add Service Plans -> Search Cloud Foundry Runtime (Done)
3. Go to Services -> Service Marketplace
4. Search Cloud Foundry runtime & open
5. Create Environment
   How to Setting Up SAP Cloud Integration (CPI) In SAP BTP
6. Go to Services -> Instances & Subscriptions
7. Klik Create
8. Isi pada field Service 'Integration Suite' & plan.
9. Go to Security -> Users -> klik
   Tutorial SAP CPI iFlow How to POST JSON to External REST API

Link yg digunakan :

1. https://developers.sap.com/tutorials/btp-integration-suite-nonsapconnectivity-settingup-suite.html
2. https://developers.sap.com/tutorials/api-mgmt-isuite-initial-setup..html#6a9b02f7-830f-495f-8405-a8ed0b483f1c
3. https://devcent-rendra.notion.site/SAP-CPI-i-suite-Restful-API-To-JSON-1bb5b7f951db804c8622d3f7a16a7073
